## Installation

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/AbhimanyuGit2507/QuotebotERP.git
cd QuotebotERP

# Backend setup
cd backend
npm install
npx prisma migrate dev
npm run start:dev

# Frontend setup
cd frontend
npm install
npm start
```

